%N A015029 Inverse of 1020th cyclotomic polynomial.
%C A015029 Periodic with period length 1020. - _Ray Chandler_, Apr 07 2017
%H A015029 Ray Chandler, <a href="/A015029/b015029.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..2000</a>
%H A015029 <a href="/index/Per#periodic">Index entries for periodic sequences</a>, period 1020.
%H A015029 <a href="/index/Rec#order_256">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, order 256.
%H A015029 <a href="/index/Pol#poly_cyclo_inv">Index to sequences related to inverse of cyclotomic polynomials</a>
%p A015029 with(numtheory,cyclotomic); c := n->series(1/cyclotomic(n,x),x,80);
%t A015029 CoefficientList[Series[1/Cyclotomic[1020,x],{x,0,120}],x] (* _Harvey P. Dale_, Jul 08 2023 *)
%o A015029 (PARI) first(n)=Vec(1/polcyclo(1020)+O(x^(n+1))) \\ _Charles R Greathouse IV_, Jun 01 2026
%K A015029 sign,easy,changed
%O A015029 0,1
%A A015029 _Simon Plouffe_
